<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١١٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3933">عَبْدَ اللهِ بْنَ مَعْقِلٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4341">عَدِيَّ بْنَ حَاتِمٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«اتَّقُوا النَّارَ وَلَوْ بِشِقِّ تَمْرَةٍ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>